Company Overview of Foxhaven Capital, LP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Foxhaven Capital, LP is a hedge fund launched and managed by Foxhaven Asset Management, LP. The fund invests in public equity and hedging markets. It employs long/short strategy to make its investments. Foxhaven Capital, LP was formed on November 1, 2013, and is domiciled in the United States.


